{"id":605,"content":"感谢!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n[Node.js correct way to make rsa encrypt?\n](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/34953732/node-js-correct-way-to-make-rsa-encrypt)\n\n经过数不清的尝试之后发现是password字段encode的格式不对导致服务端那边解不出密码\n\n这里的意思是openssl_public_encrypt()使用的填充方式和crypto.publicEncrypt默认的填充方式不一样!!\n```javascript\nconst crypto = require('crypto');\nlet password_encode = crypto.publicEncrypt(key, Buffer.from(hash + pass)).toString('base64')\n```\n修改\n```javascript\nconst crypto = require('crypto');\nconst constants = require(\"constants\");\nlet password_encode = crypto.publicEncrypt({\"key\":key,\n      padding:constants.RSA_PKCS1_PADDING}, Buffer.from(hash + pass)).toString(\"base64\");\n```\n\n","hide":"","time":"2019-02-10T06:49:41.000Z"}